message:
Hello everyone, in the past, we have been scheduling our signals to be posted at a specific time which allowed us to get massive volumes and high percentage gains very quickly. This strategy has worked for us many times in the past and allowed our members to generate millions of $ in profits over the last few years. However, the market has changed lately and we realize we need to change our strategy.

From now on, all our signals will be posted at random times without any prior notice. Whenever we see a good buying opportunity in the market, we will post it and allow our members to generate great profits quickly as well. This will allow our members to get a better entry in all our signals and allow the signals to grow organically with the market. Our team will be actively supporting all our signals as well to maximize profits for our community.

Stay tuned.

Hello everyone, in order to capitalize and maximize the results for our upcoming signal, better market conditions are needed. The market is currently not at it's optimal level and for that reason we have decided to postpone the buy signal for 1 more week. Our upcoming futures signal will now be on Sunday 13th of April 2025 instead, it will definitely be worth the wait. Stay tuned.
24 hours left until the massive futures buy signal. Tomorrow is a big day!

2 days remaining until the massive futures signal! This is a big opportunity specially since most coins are looking good to buy right now. The coin we are going to pick will be listed in the futures market on most exchanges but we mainly suggest to use Binance or Bybit for this signal.

We are officially back to signaling coins and this time we are doing things a little bit different. We have had a strong and successful track record of signaling spot coins on Cex over the last few years that have given results of up to 2000% profit and with the market changing and evolving we need to adjust accordingly. Our initial thoughts were to start signaling coins on Dex since this is where most people are trading nowadays but we will keep that thought for another day. For now, our team has decided that we are going to start signaling coins in the futures market since this is also where most of the volume is nowadays. The coins we signal will generally be listed on most exchanges since our picks will only be coins that are well established and have good fundamentals in order to ensure good liquidity for everyone regardless of bidding size. 


We have exactly 7 days to prepare for this massive futures signal which will take place on Sunday April 6 2025 at 16:00 GMT. We expect this signal to make everyone a lot of profits very quickly, stay tuned for more updates to come leading up to the signal.
